# 🎬 AlightMotion Pro (NMS)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════
http-response ^https:\/\/us-central1-alight-creative\.cloudfunctions\.net\/getAccountStatusAndLicenses script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intekaih/PremiumCC/main/Module/js/AlightMotion.js,requires-body=true,timeout=10,tag=AM-Res

